Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.35,0:00:24.30,Default,op,0,0,0,,Under the skies that are still unknown to me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.30,0:00:28.39,Default,op,0,0,0,,I know, you're doing just the same -
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.39,0:00:29.98,Default,op,0,0,0,,Dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.98,0:00:35.24,Default,op,0,0,0,,Just a small glow\NFrom those great days
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.24,0:00:38.12,Default,op,0,0,0,,Is what dragging you along
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.12,0:00:41.87,Default,op,0,0,0,,Giving you faith and some comfort
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.87,0:00:45.79,Default,op,0,0,0,,Under the sun that scorches badly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.00,0:00:52.17,Default,op,0,0,0,,I only want to see your guise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.17,0:00:53.91,Default,op,0,0,0,,But instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.91,0:00:59.18,Default,op,0,0,0,,I only watch \NWith tears on my face
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.18,0:01:04.77,Default,op,0,0,0,,As you slowly disappear in this noon haze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.77,0:01:07.76,Default,op,0,0,0,,We're alone \NWe're alone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.76,0:01:11.31,Default,op,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,1000)}Walking this world on our own
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.36,0:01:16.53,Default,op,0,0,0,,{\fade(1000,0)}Looking for each other since long ago
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.53,0:01:22.48,Default,op,0,0,0,,In the end, in the end, \NAfter the day we finally meet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.48,0:01:27.00,Default,op,0,0,0,,{\b1\bord1\blur1\t(2100,2200,\shad3\blur3\c&HABADD8&)\move(360,440,137.25,440,2200,4500)}We won't ever have to say "Goodbye"
Comment: 0,0:01:33.06,0:01:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{OP END}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.66,0:01:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:02:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What a dashing game, dear viewers!\NAnother set point is being played already!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.67,0:02:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki is aiming to finish the match quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.28,0:02:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got a champion!\NPlayer Ryuzaki wins the championship!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.88,0:02:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Ryuzaki, is there anyone, \Nwho you want to dedicate your victory to?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.68,0:02:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I dedicate it to Ms. Oka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My present shape wouldn't have been possible \Nwithout Oka's effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.95,0:02:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And why {\i1}her{\i0}, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.14,0:02:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,In this tournament, of all the girls,\Nshe was the most challenging opponent for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.62,0:02:48.60,Default,ep title,0,0,150,,{\bord4\blur15\3c&HE3C4A2&\t(0,1100,\bord0.11\blur0.4\3c&H945431&)\c&HF7EEF0&\fnGabriola\fs48\frz359.6\fscx127\fscy157}Episode 1 \N\N\NI'm even more convinced, I love you      {\fax-0.85}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.58,0:02:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone of us has a dream.\NThat's just how human nature works.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:03:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Our kind needs something to dream of.\NAnd if we don't, the life turns into an endless stream of remorse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a lot of dreams myself,\Nand I'm not giving up on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.81,0:03:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Believing in your dream isn't enough. \NYou gotta pursue it, decisively and selflessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And may I have no peace until I make sure \Nthat I have made every effort to fulfill my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.29,0:03:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Easy to say, Chiba...\N- And you are no exception!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,While your dream is still alive, \Nyou have to aspire to it! By any cost, Todo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.48,0:03:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka should come here today too, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. At 2 p.m. she is free from her studies. \NAt 3 p.m. we have training.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.81,0:03:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce, coach Katsura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.76,0:03:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,These people are from a respected \Nlocal advertising agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.27,0:03:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Since Oka is under your custody now, \Nit was you her coach who they wanted to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope I can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.32,0:04:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.40,0:04:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Katsura's trainee Oka \Nturned out to be a hidden gem,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,whose unexpected tournament triumph \Nastonished the world of women tennis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.84,0:04:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Her matches at the Japan Championship \Ndemonstrated everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.18,0:04:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,that even being unknown to anyone, \Nyou can still show great courage and achieve a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.06,0:04:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We are convinced, she'll be a perfect image \Nof how our company does its job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.59,0:04:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You should understand this more than anyone -
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.65,0:04:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're aiming to continue her growth, \Nsooner or later, you'll start working with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Will Oka... become a successful pro \Nunder your patronage?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.09,0:04:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. A lot of newbie players raised by us \Nare national heroes now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And after this tournament\NOka will undoubtedly become a pro too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, Oka. Enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.13,0:05:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But usually, we do a hundred more...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough I said.\NYou'll spare more time to rest instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.65,0:05:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I am very grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me clarify one thing right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.87,0:05:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Your work should not interfere with our training.\NThe player is distracted because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach, who were these people filming us? \NOur practice seemed so interesting to them...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not mind them.\NJust a few old acquaintances.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.64,0:05:57.64,Default,sign,0,0,30,,{\an8\b0\fnVerdana}Munakata Mansion
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Daigo. \NYou want some rice?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.12,0:06:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm completely exhausted. \NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a very...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,important day for us, Munakata.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed that lately, \Nwe mention your name less often than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get me wrong, \Nbut I'm happy with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That means... Oka, Todo, and Ochou\Nare already on the path of overcoming your death.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No more grief. No more sorrow.\NTheir hearts are open again for whatever is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It was you and you only who taught them to walk, \Nbut flying they'll have to learn themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are starting to turn into just a memory.\NBut what a bright one...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.51,0:07:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi... Are you sure? \NWon't you catch a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be alright if you prepare a hot bath for me. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.94,0:07:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, maybe you skip it just once?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.09,0:07:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible. I have to run every morning to keep fit. I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:08:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.06,0:08:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka... Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.21,0:08:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Under such heavy rain... a roadwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.87,0:08:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.41,0:08:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.54,0:08:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll catch a cold! \NHurry up and dry yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You scared me back there... \NIt was the first time I saw you that devastated...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry... I was thinking about the training,\Nforgot about everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.19,0:08:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who should apologize...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:09:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo, you are... the most clear-headed person I know...\NClear-headed! And wholesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.29,0:09:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You are equally bright, strong and good at tennis!\NAnd also handso—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why... I was so shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.26,0:09:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Oka. \NNow I'm even more convinced... I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:08.92,Default,sign,0,0,30,,{\an8\b0\fnVerdana}Ryuzaki Mansion
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Reika, isn't it time for you to come out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... I was just about to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Look here, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,According to our news sources,\Na lot of Japanese sports equipment manufacturers...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.61,0:10:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Or, at least, the three largest companies on the market\Nhave offered their sponsorship for your future career.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:30.13,Default,sign,0,0,30,,{\an8\b0\fnVerdana}Ryuzaki Reika - Successful Amateur Tennis Player
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to announce, \Nwhich one you will work with?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.09,0:10:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,As a professional, \Nhave you made up your mind upon a plan for your career?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.42,0:10:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you disappointed in becoming a pro? Do you regret \Nthe stop of your victory streak in amateur league?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.63,0:10:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, for now \Nthere's nothing I can tell for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.24,0:10:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel sorry about giving up on my win streak, \Nhowever, for now, I have nothing to tell about my plans yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My pro-career completely depends on the will \Nof my father, who is much more experienced in that matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"My pro-career completely depends \Non the will of my experienced father..."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.39,0:11:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That statement sure was amusing, Reika...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.16,0:11:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,However, have you really not decided yet, \Nexactly how your life will go on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.67,0:11:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sure that you did.\NAnd that you just chose not to share it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.97,0:11:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, since you understand this yourself, \Nplease rid me of these questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I am more concerned about Todo... \NHe is planning to leave his university's tennis club.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And as far as I know, \Nhe's leaving the university as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.99,0:11:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I knew... His resignation letter just caught my eye\N while I was taking some documents.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.21,0:11:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,In the casket, which only I have a key from, \Nmy memories will find eternal rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The hardest thing for us is finding someone intimate \Nfor the depths of our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, I can't help make your journey justified.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me... How much more of this babble am I gonna hear? \NJust show me where you hid the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.35,0:12:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,For eight years... \NI humbly suffered humiliation and ridicules.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.89,0:12:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All this time I was more of a servant for you than a wife, \Nand still, I didn't say a word!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't imagine how many dreams \NI had to put in a box and ribbon it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.74,0:12:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Aikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.87,0:12:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Maki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.46,0:12:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And after all this suffering, \NI haven't ever heard a single word of love from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.22,0:12:45.22,Default,sign,0,0,30,,{\an8\b0\fnVerdana}The Drama Club presents a play: \N"One Step to Midnight" \NStarring: Maki Aikawa
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.97,0:12:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.43,0:12:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You were so natural, Maki! \NThe last episode genuinely scared me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:13:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Maki, jokes aside! \NYou looked like you were born in this role!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.07,0:13:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing tennis didn't do the trick for me, \Nso I decided to be good at playing roles.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.36,0:13:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It will come in handy one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.91,0:13:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But "Park" is so prestigious! I really wouldn't want \Nto drop out of there, even though I don't play myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock-knock!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,However, is this indeed what thou be dreaming of?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Whichever the path thou choose, \Nthou have a future full of opportunities!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.56,0:13:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what did you want to talk about? \NYou invited me here because something bugs you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.77,0:13:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing I want to talk about. \NIt has just been a long time since we were out together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad to hear. For some reason, \Nyou looked all lost to me, Hiromi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I assume your practices are even more Aika-wild now, \Naren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.58,0:13:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,More than ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.45,0:13:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi, do you know what you'll do as a pro?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.83,0:13:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Your tennis career! \NHave you forgotten you have one now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.66,0:13:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.93,0:14:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me... You haven't thought of it even once?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep in mind... I became a pro, like, \Nfive minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.09,0:14:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,At least, you are already a real player, \Nand I'm still so far from being a real actress...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.18,0:14:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, the last subject — tennis news.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Winner of the Japan Inter-University \Namateur Championship, held last June,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.53,0:14:25.78,Default,sign,0,0,30,,{\an8\b0\fnVerdana}Todo Takayuki — Champion of University League
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.53,0:14:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo Takayuki announced \Nhis transition to the pro league.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The young champion also revealed \Nhis intention of leaving Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.74,0:14:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,to meet the world's finest pro-players \Nand come back as an experienced player.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.62,0:14:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,1000)}And now, the weather forecast...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.00,0:14:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ozaki is listening.\NYes, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.51,0:14:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What a surprising call! Long time no see. \NI am always happy to hear from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.26,0:14:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's mutual. I haven't seen you in "Park Hill" lately, \Nso I started to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.31,0:14:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, the last few weeks I had no time for tennis.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:14:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm practicing when I can. Fifty-fifty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.65,0:15:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is... This Medical Faculty exhausts me completely. \NYeah, after all this studying no energy for tennis is left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.28,0:15:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But I understand - \Nthat's not the actual reason behind your call...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.41,0:15:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,As far as I know, he wished to be left alone for a while. \NAnd that recently he stopped answering his phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.07,0:15:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened? \NI want you to tell me the whole story.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.76,0:15:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,People say he's going to some kind of journey... \NI heard, in two weeks he'll leave Japan for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.89,0:15:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Oka? \NQuit making junior mistakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.78,0:15:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.99,0:15:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,For the next two weeks, \Nyou will be practicing without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.89,0:16:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I prepared a practice menu for those two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We have mastered ball handling. \NNext is developing your physical strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.67,0:16:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't slack just because you're alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.55,0:16:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm back in two weeks, \Nyou better be through this schedule. See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.88,0:16:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me... \NBut why are you leaving so suddenly, coach?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just your coach, I don't have a duty to report to you. \NTherefore, see you in two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you at least tell me, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.62,0:16:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm heading home. \NThe shrine is going to deteriorate if it's not well cared for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,1700)}Thank you, Oka.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.74,0:16:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(1700,0)}Now I'm even more convinced... I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Successful student Todo Takayuki becomes a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The young champion is about to leave Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.81,0:17:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Oka family is listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.64,0:17:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, has anyone been asking for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.95,0:17:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Asking for you?{\i0} \NNo, there was nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure? Maybe on the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.94,0:17:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you ask?\NAre you expecting someone's call?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.07,0:17:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No, just checking to be sure... \NNevermind. Thanks for the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.50,0:17:31.48,Default,sign,0,0,20,,{\an8\b0\fnVerdana}Todo Takayuki \NIsamu Ozaki \NTakashi Chiba
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If you won't come to me, \NI will come to thee.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Todo. I can't answer the phone at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.50,0:18:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I am terribly sorry. \NThe traffic is a little crazy these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.47,0:18:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ozaki invited me to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.51,0:18:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx93}If I recall right, you managed to contact Todo and spoke to him. \NChiba, please, don't keep us waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That indeed happened. \NBut in the current situation, there's nothing we can do for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,His unusual behaviour is caused by his personal issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, can you at least tell us, where he is now? \NIt'll be unfair for you not to share his condition with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid... I have no right for that either. \NBut I can assure you there's no reason to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.27,0:18:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether he is now running, or just crawling, \Nhe made his very first step upon the road he chose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.46,0:18:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,"I don’t want to see anyone for now..." \NThat's what he told me last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,His path may be thorny, but he's obliged to walk it vigorously. \NAnd we must not interrupt his journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.67,0:18:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The Nishi High Tennis Club \Nhas changed so much after meeting coach Munakata...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.08,0:18:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is going their own way now... \NNot minding the others at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.38,0:19:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Makes sense... Ever since my graduation from Nishi High, \NI was feeling some kind of loneliness on the court.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.97,0:19:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true, Madame Butterfly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm sure Hiromi feels our connection breaking too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.94,0:19:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame Butterfly...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.76,0:19:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Two weeks is not enough to achieve anything of matter, \Nbut we'll still be doing our best. Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Every single minute is precious here. \NDon't waste 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm at your service!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,To become a pro in tennis, \Nit is not enough to just pass the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Have doubts about what you're doing - \Nforget about becoming a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.95,0:20:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Live every day like it's the last one - become a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.42,0:20:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna play with the best players the world can offer - \Nfirst prove everyone you are a real pro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.46,0:20:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo... Your path will be unbelievably difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.84,0:20:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We are bringing your tennis up to the world level! \NWhen you start hating this, don't complain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.37,0:20:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.18,0:20:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I still...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I still believe I can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, Todo! In two weeks you'll be a professional. \NAnd you will pass your pro test!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.55,0:20:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.02,0:21:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed that you train all alone for the last few days.\NAre you doing fine, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.46,0:21:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... I strive for the best no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But to be honest, \Nsuch a practice feels a little off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.94,0:21:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You can always call me out. \NI look forward to practicing with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.58,0:21:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious? I'm so grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.34,0:21:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.20,0:21:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.28,0:21:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me... Maybe it's just a rumor...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.43,0:21:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Ryuzaki, since you're on good terms with pro-world,\Nmaybe you know if what they say about Todo is true?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.12,0:21:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Had that been a misconception, \Nyou'd be the first one to know, Hiromi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.47,0:21:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach Munakata raised us all. \NIf it wasn't for him, we wouldn't have tennis and all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.71,0:21:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what he said.
Comment: 0,0:22:10.29,0:22:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{ED START}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.92,0:22:22.67,Default,ed,0,0,0,,There is one song I cannot ever forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.67,0:22:28.30,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Still, there's a face I'm willing to forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.30,0:22:31.26,Default,ed,0,0,0,,With her feelings messed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.26,0:22:34.14,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Alice got completely lost
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.14,0:22:39.33,Default,ed,0,0,0,,The midst of summer \NBrought her into one tricky love maze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.65,0:22:46.24,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I want you to hug tightly\NAnd never let go of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.24,0:22:51.62,Default,ed,0,0,0,,One scared and timid tiny girl
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.62,0:22:58.50,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I quite remember our very first kiss \NAnd the beginning of all of this
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.08,0:23:04.92,Default,ed,0,0,0,,While birds were singing for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.99,0:23:14.11,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I'll take a car and take a lonely trip
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.11,0:23:19.31,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I know it'll bring me \NTo the seashore
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.31,0:23:22.36,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Where only the the sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.36,0:23:25.40,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Dazzlingly bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.40,0:23:30.93,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Could witness my long-awaited happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.40,0:23:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Aikawa Maki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.43,0:23:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We're now on our way to the seaside training camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.00,0:23:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna make the most of\Nour 19th summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.21,0:23:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But for Hiromi this summer will be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.52,0:23:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo suddenly takes the undreamed path.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.27,0:23:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for Hiromi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.06,0:23:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, to do this, Todo even asked Coach Katsura for a special training.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.05,0:23:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But, coach, why do you keep saying that Todo is not young enough now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.61,0:24:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming soon: "My 19th summer."
